description: Total number of multiple edges in all essentially parallel series-parallel networks with n labeled edges, multiple edges allowed.
references: J. W. Moon, Some enumerative results on series-parallel networks, Annals Discrete Math., 33 (1987), 199-226 (the sequence M_P(n)*P_pi).
links: Index entries for sequences mentioned in Moon (1987)
formula: E.g.f. = (exp(-x)-1+x)*P'(x), where P(x) = e.g.f. for A000311.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 20 2000
